<br>
This game is amazing.  It has great music and the best graphics ever.  The anime cutscenes blended with the 3D rendered mechs is amazing.  I have never seen a game like this.  The control and fluid motion of Jehuty is riveting.  And this was only the demo.  I long for this game to come out.  Everyone who remotly likes 3rd person games should check this game out.  This game will become an instant legend and seen as a step above all other games.  Also there are many more one on one orbital frame battles then the first one.  Those are the greatest battles of all.  If you dont believe that this is amazing fo to konami.com/2ndrunner and download the Tokyo Game Show preview.  Also, for anyone who is curious the song played in the background of it is called Beyond the Bounds.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=melch14>melch14</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(2/23/03 4:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=609.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/melch49/zzguy.txt height=110 width=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Zone of the Enders: The 2nd Runner. Best game ever!!!!</span><hr size=1> I, too, played the 2nd Runner demo. I really liked it. The graphics are great to look at and run incredibly smooth.<br>
