<br>
Anyway, the combat is flawless and hardcore.  This is one intense game and its not just random button smashing. You have to block fast and attack faster. The controls are tight and there is no bad camera angles.<br>
<br>
The graphics and gameplay would make a great game by them selves but it doesnt end there.  There is the story which is told between anime cutscenes(which rock), computer rendered cutscenes(which rock), and little image transmission screens( which prove to be quite interesting).  The story is about war, love, vengence, annialation, and domination of power.  All of which are done beautifully.  <br>
<br>
Then to add to the story is the great cast.  Featuring familiar people like Leo from the first one(whos not just some stupid annoying kid anymore), and new people like almost everyone else.  I suppose Nohman was in the first since he pilots Anubis even though I dont think he was ever called Nohman.  Viola is also sort of back.  The voices are great and very fitting of each character.<br>
<br>
Then aside from the regular game, 2 player mode returns and I believe there are some additional missions.  Im not sure because I havent beaten the game yet so i dont even have the two player mode so I dont know if its better than the first ones two player mode.  I would think it would be since its going to have a lot more characters to choose.<br>
<br>
Seriously people, this is honostly the most perfect game I have ever played.  Nothing is bad and everything is great.  I you didnt hate the first one buy this one.  If you enjoy third person games buy this before anything else. I recommend it to everyone. I suppose you could wait for the reviews or see what I say once I have beaten the game, but why wait.  I can tell you right now, dont be surpised when you see perfect ratings and I sure the game will be game of the month in every magazine that rates PS2 games.  Im sure I will rate it perfect as well.    <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=agentcryrid>Agent Cryrid</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(3/16/03 3:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=609.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: i got it</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The controls are tight and there is no bad camera angles.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
